msgid "Routing Configuration"
msgstr "路由設定"

msgid ""
"Optional warehouse routing for multi-warehouse setups. Lower priority "
"numbers = higher priority for routing."
msgstr "可選的倉庫路由設定，適用於多倉庫配置。優先級數字越低，路由優先級越高。"

